  ('investigation-d5dfc642-moex-00184', 'investigation-d5dfc642', 'investigation-d5dfc642-moex-110-916530c6', 'sub-investigation-d5dfc642-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲、乙為男女朋友，因分手爭吵。甲打電話到乙家告訴乙之母親，限當
